casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Laux.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Laux (1990), 55 Ohio St. 3d 602.]

(No. 90-1820 Submitted October 3, 1990 Decided October 10, 1990.)

The resignation of Richard Stephen Laux as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
